{"error":0,"message":"","data":[{"show_ID":"1875","airdate":"1488913200","name_switch":"off","DJ":"ziona","showname":"Tuesday of your first or all-time favourites!","blurb":"Hey all Slayers around! \n\nWhat if that Tuesday everyone would request either one of his\/her ALL-TIME favourites ever made, or your FIRST remix \/ SID \/ demoscene tune ever, what you fell in love with, maybe even took you here? :) \n\nOther requests are also welcomed, but let's try to focus, because I'm curious about your taste, and I'll place my own bets too for some tracks! \n\nAnd it turned out we'll have a special Slayer-guest showing up too: let me introduce you Vegan64 a bit! ","nice_showname":"<strong><big>ziona<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Tuesday of your first or all-time favourites!","nice_airdate":"Tuesday 7th March, 2017<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"1877","airdate":"1488999600","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Bozzy and the Bint","showname":"BBKB","blurb":"It's the Taint of the Week\u2122 again, so it's time for Boz to utter complete bollocks in between your requests. Thankfully, Kate is here to translate some of it into English. All aboard the Train-Wreck, WOO WOOH!","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Bozzy and the Bint<\/big><\/strong><br \/>BBKB","nice_airdate":"Wednesday 8th March, 2017<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"1876","airdate":"1489086000","name_switch":"off","DJ":"KraxxUltima","showname":"The Uncracked Tracks","blurb":"Well ,last weeks show went really well soundwise, so let's go full force. Taking on your Commodore requests as usual and playing the occasional weird ones as well. Tune in and most importantly have fun =)","nice_showname":"<strong><big>KraxxUltima<\/big><\/strong><br \/>The Uncracked Tracks","nice_airdate":"Thursday 9th March, 2017<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"}]}